defaultProfessor defaultAnsaridefault:default The potential of a change in the direction of relations and the potential for positive developments could be quite dramatic. 
defaultBritain
default has always had interests in 
defaultIran
default. We know that Anglo-Iranian relations have not always been terribly positive, but they have not necessarily been quite as disastrous as some of the naysayers would like us to think. I certainly think that the Russian relationship was probably worse in many respects, and yet they have managed to surmount their history, so it is possible for 
defaultBritain
