defaultQ46 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default How good are we in the 
defaultUK
default at reading 
defaultIran
default? How do we compare now with the past?
defaultProfessor defaultAnsaridefault:default In the past there has been an enormous resource base in not only the Foreign Office but the numerous companies that have had origins in 
defaultIran
